Iga '''Asif n sus''' yan wasif illan ɣ iffus n tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Ila bahra atig ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]]. Aɣbalu n wasif ad illa ɣ idrarn n [[Aṭlas mqqurn|Waṭlaṣ mqqurn]]. A izruy f [[Awluz]] d Hwara nɣ Wlad tayma d sin timdinin istawhman ɣ Sus atnt igan [[Tarudant]] d [[Ayt Mllul]]. Tiɣzi nns tlkm 190 m. 

== Aẓur n yism ==
Asif ad ar izray f mnnaw idɣarn ɣ ammas n tmazirt n [[Sus]], ig ula iwtta ngr tiɣrmt n [[Ayt Mllul]] d [[Inzggan]] ; sin timdinin mqqurnin d stawhman ɣ tasga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]]. Ɣayn af as gan ism ad n Asif n Sus.

